pageContext.claim: “For the last 47 years Sleepy Joe Biden shipped away your jobs, shut down your factories, threw open your borders, and ravaged our cities while sacrificing American blood and treasure in these endless, ridiculous foreign wars. In countries you never even heard of. Joe Biden is a servant of the left wing globalists and lobbyists, the wealthy donors, the Washington vultures who got rich bleeding America dry.”
pageContext.analysis: This is ridiculous over-the-top rhetoric, a smear on hyperdrive.
